region.description: The AWS region the bucket is located in

accessKeyId.description: The AWS Access Key ID to use to access the S3 Bucket, alternatively set the AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID environment variable

secretAccessKey.description: The AWS Secret Access Key to use to access the S3 Bucket, alternatively set the AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY environment variable

bucket.description: The the name of the S3 Bucket to store the Nx Cache in

forcePathStyle.description: Set to true to use path style URLs for S3 objects
